Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是吗  史蒂夫  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- didn't we, Steve? - Yeah, I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们是为了自卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we were defending ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我们要防的却是他这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It turns out we were defending ourselves from people like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当时不知道自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He didn't know what he was doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在每天都注射药物  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He takes his medication every day, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  他曾有些精神错乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, at one time he was unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他现在正常了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But... he's back to normal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你怎么了  儿子  -没事啊  爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's going on, son? - Nothing, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这副样子我没法看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't look at him when he's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉伦·沃克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kieren Walker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你被捕了  -被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're under arrest. - Arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天有人闯进诊所  放走了狂暴僵尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}GP's were broke into yesterday, rabids were let loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僵尸攻击了接待员  她入院了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They attacked the receptionist, she's in hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天哪  -闯进诊所的不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jesus! - I didn't break into the GP's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我解释也没用  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not me who needs convincing. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要带他去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, hey, where are you taking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教区理事会要问他话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Parish council want to question him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不能就这样把他拖过去啊  -苏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can't just drag him off like this. - Sue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马丁小姐吩咐的  我必须带他过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orders from Miss Martin. I've got to bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸  妈  -你就这么傻站着吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mum? Dad? - Are you just going to stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说去就得去啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What she says goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听我说完吗  我是想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you just give me a second, please? I am trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}忘记用药一次就会发生以下情形\N警惕狂暴征兆\N不由自主的颤抖\N流鼻血\N失忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事的  没事没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're fine, you're fine, you're fine, you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"您正在收听诺顿调频  在诺顿村为您播报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You're listening to Roar FM, coming to you from down the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"今日首个话题当然就是《苦斗》"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"First topic of the day is, of course, Hard Graft."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不不  -"现在我们..."\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Oh, no, no, no. - "Now we..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-出什么事了  马丁女士  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's wrong, Ms Martin? - I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你倒杯茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get you a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清官难断家务事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Parents can be the living end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不常跟我父亲说话  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't speak to my father very often, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次说话  那真是一言难尽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I do, it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢跟我爸妈说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't like talking to mine neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是说个没完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're always jabbering on and on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子永远插不上嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can never get a word in edgeways
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到走运才难得能跟我兄弟说上几句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm lucky if I get to speak to my brother once in a blue moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我有个兄弟  -是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I have a brother. - Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥还是弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Older or younger?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他同我很亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's very dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最需要亲人的时候  他们从来不在  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're never around when you need them most, though, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他的共犯在哪  -到处都找遍了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where's his accomplice? - Looked all over for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影儿都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马丁女士坚持要他俩一起受审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ms Martin was very insistent that they were tried together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跑了我们能怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What can we do if he's scarpered?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就你来交代吧  -交代什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Let's hear it from you, then. - Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我没什么要认的  -胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Nothing to confess. - Rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那个爱尔兰佬闯进诊所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and that Irish one broke into the GP's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放掉的狂暴僵尸袭击了接待员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and let loose rabids that mauled the receptionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被人引入歧途让我心痛不已  吉伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It saddens me that you've been so led astray, Kieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击之后  有人见到你和你的共犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your accomplice were seen coming out of the GP's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从诊所出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}after the mauling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和西蒙几天前一起在诊所工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Me and Simon worked together at the GP's a couple of days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就再也没去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we haven't been back since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢在治疗中心的日子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you enjoy your time at the treatment centre?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不认罪的话  就得回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cos that's where you're headed if you don't confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不能送我回诺福克  -要打赌吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can't send me back to Norfolk! - Want to bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"如果半死症患者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"If a PDS sufferer is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"被怀疑违反了释放条例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"suspected of breaching their terms of release,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"须依照条例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"they must be reported
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"上报至半死症事务部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"to the Department of Partially Deceased Affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"不合作的病人随后将被拘留\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"whereupon the non-compliant patient will be detained
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"以防危害自身或他人安全"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"for their own safety and the safety of others."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有违反释放条例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't breached my terms of release.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"对自身或公众安危构成威胁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"PDS patients who pose a threat to themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"半死症患者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"or members of their community
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"将被视为危险分子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"are considered dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"须通知有关部门"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"and the proper authorities should be notified."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的共犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your accomplice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被认定对公众构成了威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have been deemed a threat to your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我对公众不构成威胁  -你是社区吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm not a threat to the community. - Are you the community?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我是公...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I am the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白你要问什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你  你是公众吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm asking you, are you the community?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是  -没错  你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - That's right, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是公众\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are the community
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们认为你对其构成了威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we have deemed you a threat to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖认罪 我们就给你缓刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, admit your guilt and we'll hand you a suspended sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就回诺福克吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's off to Norfolk you go.
