Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上班要迟到了  我还以为你能待在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm late for work. I was hoping you could stop in.
