Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我很担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Well, I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"今日一篇报道半死症患者产生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"There's a piece in paper today about these PDS sufferers
