Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是随手修修东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just doing a spot of DIY.
