Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯狂高尔夫可是技巧性运动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Crazy golf is a game of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然怎么会是奥运会比赛项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wouldn't be an Olympic sport if it wasn't.
