Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是因为名字叫"疯狂高尔夫"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe because it's called "Crazy golf."
