Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没准把打疯狂高尔夫的人聚在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps if the crazy golf people got together
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想个严肃点的名字  比如...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and came up with a more serious-sounding name, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复杂障碍高尔夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}elaborate obstacle golf,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时你再看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you see then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许奥组委就会把它算作体育项目了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then the olympic body might make it a proper sport.
