Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群破神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stupid gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我感觉不到  不觉得冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's OK. I don't feel anything. Don't feel the cold.
