Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.27,0:24:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全没知觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't feel a bloody thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.80,0:24:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也经常忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I forget meself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.04,0:25:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么急干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the rush?
