Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.93,0:43:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.00,0:43:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.80,0:44:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}吉伦·沃克  亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.45,0:44:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-艾米  -进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Amy? - In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.18,0:44:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到你的留言了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.53,0:44:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.93,0:44:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你的帐篷顶上扯破了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know you've got a tear at the top of your tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.99,0:45:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我要做的大事比  这微不足道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Small potatoes in the grand scheme of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.97,0:45:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是该带个睡袋来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was I supposed to bring a sleeping bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.65,0:45:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复生的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}During the Rising...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.33,0:45:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀过狂暴僵尸吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}did you ever kill a rabid?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.96,0:45:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复生时  我是搞后勤的那种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}During the Rising, I was more a back office sort of bloke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.84,0:45:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀过也没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's ok if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.60,0:45:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能杀过更好点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Actually, it's better if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.72,0:45:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我谁都没杀过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I never killed anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.85,0:45:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有帮人安乐死过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not even a sort of... mercy killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.26,0:45:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.80,0:45:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我戴上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put them on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.58,0:46:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着螺丝刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pick up the screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.68,0:46:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先告诉我你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not until you tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.95,0:46:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um... I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.90,0:46:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经在5号登机楼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm currently at Terminal 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.78,0:46:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李箱都收拾好了  我在候机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got my suitcase packed, I'm in the departure lounge,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.34,0:46:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差上飞机了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just need to get on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.81,0:46:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.31,0:46:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.24,0:46:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对药物产生了免疫性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've become immune to the medication,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.06,0:46:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我都没有药效了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the drugs aren't working any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.23,0:46:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快我就会恢复狂暴状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And not long from now, I'm going to go rabid,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.26,0:46:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且没有药物可以再让我变回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and there's no chemicals out there that can turn me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.78,0:46:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想变回狂暴僵尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to live as a rabid,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.43,0:46:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行尸走肉  到处害人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}going around hurting people without a thought in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.08,0:46:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种日子太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's no kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.49,0:46:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去给罗素医生打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll call Dr.Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.59,0:46:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的  一旦我变了就变不回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's no good. Once I turn, I turn for good and then I'm stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.73,0:46:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远那样活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stuck like that for ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.76,0:46:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生不如死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a fate worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.73,0:47:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你得在我变之前杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why I need you to put me down before I go rabid.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.01,0:47:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊  求您给我一个启示吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lord, please, give me a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.35,0:47:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.72,0:47:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了  马丁女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry to disturb, Miss Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.36,0:47:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was just wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.99,0:47:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是否想下来一起看大结局呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you wanted to come downstairs for the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.54,0:47:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-大结局  -我追的侦探片《苦斗》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Finale? - Me detective show - Hard Graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.50,0:47:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连锁超市最好的卡瓦酒  专为今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shop'n'Save's best cava for the big night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.51,0:47:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莱夫  你不用这么费心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Clive, you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.43,0:47:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是重要场合  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a big occasion, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.30,0:47:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《苦斗》的最后一集了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Final episode of Hard Graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.10,0:47:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是昨晚播的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That were on last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.46,0:47:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  妈妈  但桑德拉昨晚没看上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, Mum, but Sandra didn't get to watch it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.89,0:47:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我录下来了  我们今晚看好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I recorded it and we're watching it tonight, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.31,0:47:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Too bloody right we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.75,0:47:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.89,0:48:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于能知道凶手是谁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I get to find out who the killer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.14,0:48:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也很激动  马丁女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you excited, too, Miss Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.38,0:48:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都坐不住了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Edge of me seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.02,0:48:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.97,0:48:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在屋里躲了一天呢  对吧克莱夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've not been out of the house all day, have I, Clive?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.46,0:48:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把自己锁在卧室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She locked herself in bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.45,0:48:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时前才出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}didn't come out till an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.09,0:48:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怕听到剧透呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just in case I heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.68,0:48:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都别想破坏今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've made sure that nothing can spoil it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.86,0:48:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.70,0:48:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑德拉  你没给妈妈倒酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandra, you left out Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.34,0:48:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不喝酒  她不能喝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She don't drink. She can't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.42,0:48:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会跟上次一样穿肠而过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll go through you like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.26,0:48:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝一杯没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.95,0:48:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-桑德拉  给她一杯吧  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sandra, give her a glass, eh? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.72,0:48:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时后  还得我去收拾她的烂摊子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cos in an hour I'll be cleaning up her mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.24,0:48:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没戏  今晚不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No way. Not tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.71,0:48:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我最大  什么都不给她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tonight's my night. She gets nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.03,0:48:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探长约翰·格莱福特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Detective Inspector John Graft,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.16,0:48:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  魁梧粗犷的约克郡男子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thank you, you rugged Yorkshire hunk of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.93,0:48:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们所有人的生活都添了些许精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for bringing a little bit of excitement into all our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.79,0:48:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看节目吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now on with the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.61,0:48:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手是约翰·格莱福特的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}John Graft's dad is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.32,0:48:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚看了大结局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw the finale last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.62,0:48:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手一直是约翰·格莱福特的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turns out John Graft's dad were the killer all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.69,0:48:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前任警长就是他杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was the one who killed the ex-police captain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.99,0:49:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为80年代的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}cos back in the '80s,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.43,0:49:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长打遍了和他一起筑人墙的好哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the captain beat up all the dad's mates on the picket line.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.94,0:49:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老早就看出神转折了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Saw that plot twist a mile off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.56,0:49:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早说过这剧很狗血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Told you it was silly buggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.61,0:49:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个邪恶的老巫婆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You rotten, evil hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.15,0:49:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-桑德拉  -闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sandra... - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.13,0:49:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个十八层地狱里来的魔鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You, you're a devil sent from the bowels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.64,0:49:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从那天晚上起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ever since that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.88,0:49:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从看见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ever since that night
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从坟墓里爬出来的那天晚上起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I saw you rise out of your grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.74,0:49:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无时不刻地折磨着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you've been a torment to me.
